        Initialises a new artillery shell. All coordinates are in world-space.
        Parameters:
        x - Starting x coordinate.
        y - Starting y coordinate.
        target - Coordinates of the target.
        inaccuracy - A radius of inaccuracy in world-units.
        archingFactor - How much the shell arches in the air.
